# V-COND — CONDITION-INVARIANCE via realistic augmentation + GATED FiLM.
# Perturbs ONLY timing channels (IAT/jitter) + occasional packet drop — NEVER
# sizes/directions (identity signal protected -> prevents forgetting).
# Realistic: latency-scale, correlated jitter, queuing-gap, mild loss.
# Validates on: (1) clean CESNET (must hold), (2) HEAVILY-perturbed CESNET
# (the clean invariance metric), (3) Korean 5G (real, cosine-robust, confounded).
